column5: Do any of you have suggestions on good ones to stay at or ones to stay away from? Thanks
check out Kenora days inn. been staying there for years and never had any problems. phone807-468-2003
We have stayed at the Comfort Inn, excellent and economical. It is next to Tim Hortons and just up the road from the Anisinabe campground boat launch.
Thanks for the help. I called today and got our rooms. I wanted to make sure I had a place to put my head after a 1000 mile day.
